<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Web相关 - Category - w23ta0's blog</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/web%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/</link><description>This is my new Hugo FixIt site</description><generator>Hugo 0.145.0 &amp; FixIt v0.3.16</generator><language>en</language><managingEditor>wt8566958@gmail.com (w23ta0)</managingEditor><webMaster>wt8566958@gmail.com (w23ta0)</webMaster><lastBuildDate>Sat, 08 Mar 2025 01:23:27 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/web%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>使用 CSS 实现标题自动编号</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/2015/10/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-css-%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E7%BC%96%E5%8F%B7/</link><pubDate>Fri, 23 Oct 2015 18:27:00 +0000</pubDate><author>wt8566958@gmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/2015/10/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8-css-%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98%E8%87%AA%E5%8A%A8%E7%BC%96%E5%8F%B7/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/web%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/">Web相关</category><description>&lt;p>近几天在学习 HTML5 与 CSS3 时，偶然看到了 CSS 中自动为标题添加编号的特性。仔细阅读过 W3Schools 上提供的文档之后，试验了一下，确实非常好用。从此不需再花费精力校对标题编号，可以将时间集中到真正需要做的事情，也避免了手动编号出错的窘态。&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>LoadRunner 11 安装及破解</title><link>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/2015/08/loadrunner-11-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8F%8A%E7%A0%B4%E8%A7%A3/</link><pubDate>Thu, 20 Aug 2015 13:14:53 +0000</pubDate><author>wt8566958@gmail.com (w23ta0)</author><guid>https://w23ta0.github.io/posts/2015/08/loadrunner-11-%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%8F%8A%E7%A0%B4%E8%A7%A3/</guid><category domain="https://w23ta0.github.io/categories/web%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3/">Web相关</category><description>&lt;h2 id="前提条件" class="heading-element">&lt;span>前提条件&lt;/span>
